akn:section.akn:heading: Lands held in private, municipal, or State ownership not affected

akn:content.akn:p: § 194. Lands held in private, municipal, or State ownership not affected No lands located within the park boundaries held in private, municipal, or State ownership on January 26, 1915, shall be affected by or subject to the provisions of sections 191, 193, 195, and 195a of this title. (Jan. 26, 1915, ch. 19, § 3, 38 Stat. 800.)
